        public static Person updatePerson(java.sql.Connection conn,
                                  int id,
                                  java.lang.String firstName,

                                  int addressId,
                                  int occupationId)
        Connects to the MySQL server and updates a person with a user inputed id and checks to make sure that the new person doesn't already exist in the database. If successful at updating the person the new person will be returned
        Parameters:
        conn - The MySQL connection
        id - The ID of the person to update
        firstName - The new first name of the person to be updated blank if keeping the old first name
        middleName - The new middle name of the person to be updated blank if keeping the old middle name
        lastName - The new last name of the person to be updated blank if keeping the old last name
        homePhone - The new home phone of the person to be updated blank if keeping the old home phone
        mobilePhone - The new mobile phone name of the person to be updated blank if keeping the old mobile phone
        workPhone - The new work phone of the person to be updated blank if keeping the old work phone
        homeEmail - The new home email of the person to be updated blank if keeping the old home email
        workEmail - The new work email of the person to be updated blank if keeping the old work email
        height - The new height of the person to be updated blank if keeping the old height
        weight - The new weight of the person to be updated blank if keeping the old weight
        gender - The new gender of the person to be updated blank if keeping the old gender
        race - The new race of the person to be updated blank if keeping the old race
        addressId - The new address ID of the person to be updated blank if keeping the old address ID
        occupationId - The new occupation ID of the person to be updated blank if keeping the old occupation ID
        Returns:
        The updated person if successful if not null is returned
